Clément Sibony https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cl%C3%A9ment_Sibony 0 Clément Sibony (born 30 November 1976) is a French actor and film director. He has appeared in more than 60 films and television shows since 1991. He won the award for Best Actor at the 22nd Moscow International Film Festival for his role in Taking Wing.
